===Falun Dafa===

{{main|Falun (symbol)}}

In [[Falun Gong]] or [[Falun Dafa]], the Fǎlún (法轮) is described as “an intelligent, rotating entity composed of high-energy matter.” Practitioners of Falun Gong cultivate this Law Wheel, which rotates constantly in the lower abdomen, the same focal point described as [[Dantian#Three_dantians|Lower Dāntián]].

